{
  "stem": "12868.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the Germans-- Germans took me away with all the sick, with all the dead people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They think, you're-- I'm already dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they put me in a big-- in a big train like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then, later on, the-- the Americans-- they see already the Americans coming in, they throw out all the dead-- when you see on the picture there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they think I am dead, too, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they came to make movies, for the films, the dead-- thousands of thousands.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They found some of them moving, me and two more, me and two more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Matter of fact, when I came here in Atlanta, I found them the third one, was-- was liberated the same like me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I-- he was the third one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We hugged each other.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We kissed each other here in Atlanta.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Anyway, but I didn't remember my liberation because I'd been in like, a coma, where the-- you know, if the American Army came with-- with a half hour later, I'd be already between the dead, you see.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they tried to bring somebody-- somebody moving.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Maybe they tried to bring alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And they brought-- they took out me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They took me like a piece of wood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "My weight was 39 pounds.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And they put me in the nearest hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They call it Saint Ottilien, in a German hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And-- and-- and they put me there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I-- I didn't remember this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "This was the-- the American Army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They showed me where they liberate me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "They give me all the informations of how they found me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "When I opened up my eyes, I see around me soldiers and-- and nurses, white nurses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I've never see American uniforms-- you know, army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I thought the Germans found out I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
